ech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale &quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊设备上黑色星期五的最佳早期优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday &quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;现在最值得购买的 Sonos 扬声器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23507492/sonos-best-speaker-one-roam-move- Five- arc-beam-ray-sub&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;oOhnyc&quot;>;首先，现在您可以购买 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/23656561/sonos-era-100-speaker-review-features&quot;>;&lt;strong>;Sonos Era 100 智能音箱&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;，售价 199 美元（折扣 50 美元），&lt;a href=&quot; https://howl.me/ck1vXfj3dND&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;并直接来自&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https:// /www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/era-100&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Sonos&lt;/a>;。今年早些时候发布的新款 Sonos 智能音箱取代了旧款 Sonos One。与 One 相比，Sonos Era 100 凭借以下新功能提供了更好的声音...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965566/ sonos-era-100-roam-arc-beam-soundbar-smart-speaker-black-friday-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965566/sonos-era-100-roam-arc-beam-soundbar-smart-speaker-black-friday-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23965566/sonos-era-100-roam-arc-beam-soundbar-smart-speaker-black-friday-deal-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T13:11:12-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T13:11:12-05:00</updated><title>您现在可以购买的最佳早期黑色星期五科技产品优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;明亮的彩色矢量插图，显示一只手穿过门去抓产品。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3BEs4McVGb5-HJWXlIbINlpBsP8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72817910/236878_BLACK_FRIDAY_STILL_GET_AFernand ez.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7VqosP&quot;>;官方消息：2023 年提前假日购物季已经到来。如果您想在假日购物中抢占先机，请选择 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/blackfriday?ref_=nav_cs_td_bfc_dt_cr&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot; https://goto.target.com/c/482924/81938/2092?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.target.com%2Fc%2Ftarget-black-friday%2F-%2FN-5q0f2&amp;sharedid=theverge .com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Target&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckUHCBbD1E5&quot;>;百思买&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href= “https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fshop%2Fdeals%2Fblack-friday&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com”rel=&quot;赞助的 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>; 已经推出了早期的黑色星期五促销活动，降低了平板电脑、无线耳机、笔记本电脑、智能家居技术，甚至 OLED 电视的价格。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class =&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;pf8Whf&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot; title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{ &quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 100 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget&quot;} ,{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget &quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊设备上黑色星期五的最佳早期优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday &quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;黑色星期五耳机和耳塞的最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber -monday&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;3cCHYD&quot;>;随着 11 月 24 日的临近，我们可能会看到更多优惠，但到目前为止有哪些折扣还是非常值得一看的。例如，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort-Bluetooth-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B098FKXT8L/?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose 降噪 QuietComfort 45 耳机&lt;/a>; 及其新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort-Cancelling-World-Class-Cancellation/dp/B0CD2FSRDD ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞&lt;/a>; 已跌至历史新低。一系列其他小工具和小玩意也在促销，来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Google-Pixel-Buds-Pro-Headphones/dp/B0B1N7SGMZ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel =&quot;provided nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Google Pixel Buds Pro&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/ckUoga3ETYj&quot;>;15 英寸 MacBook Air&lt;/a>; 到新款超薄笔记本...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23899698/best-early-black-friday-tech-deals-amazon-target-best-buy-walmart-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>布兰登·威德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T13:05:58-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T13:05:58-05:00</updated><title>黑色星期五耳机和耳塞的最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 WF-1000XM5 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/A7rrd_bVzx_597Wpg7ndNjQxfr8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72876575/DSCF2223.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;XXP47s&quot;>;令人难以抗拒的假日促销已经正式到来，许多来自最大科技品牌的耳机和耳塞均打折至黑色星期五和网络星期一的最低价格。正如您所看到的，早在这两个疯狂的购物日之前就已经有大量优惠活动了。如果您一直在推迟购买 Apple、Sony、Samsung、Google 和其他品牌的商品，那么您可能不会比 2023 年黑色星期五的优惠更好。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;y4FImf&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique- tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 100 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech- ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best- Cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;nZTcKO&quot;>;我预计最大的耳机制造商不会很快推出任何重大新产品，因此，如果您决定参与以下任何交易，则无需担心买家会后悔。进入寒冷的月份，总是值得的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-星期一&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965357/black-friday-2023-headphone-earbuds-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T13:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T13:00:00-05:00</updated><title>屏幕确实不错</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;浅色运动衫上人性化 AI 徽章的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gE6xDaEAWbysG2v_rhT30ZR1E6U=/0x0:2240x1493/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72876516/Humane_Ai_Pin_Business.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;这东西到底是如何向我展示一张有趣的猫图片的，这样我就可以暂时摆脱参观的苦差事DMV？&lt;/em>; |图片：Humane&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3W1Cp9&quot;>;上周，Humane 推出了 AI Pin，作为无屏幕手机的替代品。你可以通过语音与它互动，一个微型投影仪会在你的手掌上显示媒体控制和来电等内容。我们的想法是让您轻松地穿越世界，不受不断需要您关注的数字设备的阻碍。佩戴 AI Pin 就意味着生活在屏幕之外的世界。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;DJCty0&quot;>;这是一个我很乐意接受的美好愿景。但事情是这样的：屏幕很棒，我认为我们还不能，甚至不应该完全抛弃它们。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;cPKs01&quot;>;Humane 的整个交易集中在其无屏幕性上。产品——创始人 Imran Chaudhri 在他的 TED 演讲中说了同样的话今年早些时候&lt;/a>;。在 Humane 看来，屏幕是我们之间的障碍......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965540/ humane-ai-pin-screen-phone-ambient-computing &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965540/humane-ai-pin-screen-phone-ambient-computing" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965540/ humane-ai-pin-screen-phone-ambient-computing</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T11:48:27-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T11:48:27-05:00</updated><title>乔·拜登的首席气候顾问谈气候变化将如何影响美国经济</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;阿里·扎伊迪在讲台上讲话，身后的墙上有美国国旗和白宫标志&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uVDHN5jzMG9XgzwNQGtPyEL-1fc= /0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72876135/P20211216CS_1202.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;国家气候顾问 Ali Zaidi 于 12 月星期四举行新闻发布会2021 年 10 月 16 日，白宫詹姆斯·S·布雷迪新闻发布会室。图片：白宫&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;RielOa&quot;>;气候变化已经开始&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/14/23958824/us -national-climate-assessment-unequal-costs-climate-change&quot;>;根据最全面的全国性&lt;a href=&quot;https://nca2023.globalchange.gov/&quot;>;评估，美国经济受到的影响&lt;/a>; &lt;/a>; 但这是本周早些时候发布的。这是每四年进行一次的国家气候评估，将整个章节专门用于经济学。其“保守估计”是极端天气&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/8/9/22613531/climate-change-united-nations-report-extreme-weather-ipcc&quot;>;增压&lt;/a>; 全球变暖每年已造成 1500 亿美元的损失。这只是我们不断变化的地球将如何影响美国人的钱包的一个例子。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;NjcfHt&quot;>;&lt;q>;极端天气增压全球变暖每年造成1500亿美元的损失&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Fw6lg1&quot;>;拜登政府如何应对这一新现实？人工智能等新技术对这一事业是有帮助还是有害？ &lt;em>;The Verge &lt;/em>;与阿里交谈...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963681/biden-climate-adviser-climate-change-us -economy-ali-zaidi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23963681/biden-climate-adviser-climate-change-us-economy-ali-zaidi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23963681/biden-climate-adviser-climate-change-us-economy-ali-zaidi</id><author><name>贾斯汀·卡尔玛</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T10:15:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T10:15:00-05:00</updated><title> 《君主：怪物的遗产》的创作者不仅仅是想制作一部哥斯拉衍生剧</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个巨大的类似恐龙的生物从雾墙中咆哮。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7uRSJgQleIHn9Dzkf-9hFPUQzZs=/0x0:2199x1466/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875762/Monarch_Legacy_of_Monsters_Photo_010104 .0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Monarch 联合创作者 Chris Black 和 Matt Fraction 以及导演 Matt Shakman 讲述了为什么他们的新 MonsterVerse 系列如此关注普通人类。&lt;/p >; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23960969/monarch-legacy-of-monsters-matt-shakman-matt-fraction-chris-black-interview</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T10:01:54-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T10:01:54-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 为妈妈们准备的 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/L6N2nmWpZ-tCeYFFnr6LkNtS70I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875697/236830_FOR_MOMS_Gift_Guide_ Artboards_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列炫酷、平静且富有创意的礼物，以表达您对生活中特殊母亲形象的欣赏.&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:46:20-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:46:20-05:00</updated><title>这是一款让你过上低调生活的键盘</title><content type="html">&lt;p>;Lofree Flow 是一款低调的键盘，打字和听起来都像全高键盘。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow -low-profile-keyboard-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review</id><author><name>丹·塞弗特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>凯迪拉克新款 Optiq 紧凑型电动 SUV 将是最便宜的电动汽车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;橙色凯迪拉克 SUV，顶部涂成黑色，位于玻璃面板建筑前&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4ZB7B8Q9Mqb1FQO3FCZZADJjXNE=/0x0:6325x4217/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875439/MY24_CADILLAC_OPTIQ_SPORT_GMCA0740.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Optiq，你到底有多便宜？&lt;/em>; |图片：凯迪拉克&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X2AwUB&quot;>;凯迪拉克宣布推出一款名为 Optiq 的新型电动汽车，据称该车型将“作为该汽车制造商在美国的电动汽车产品线的切入点”。此前，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23522467/cadillac-lyriq-ev-review-specs-photos-price&quot;>;售价 64,000 美元的凯迪拉克 Lyriq&lt;/a>; 是该汽车制造商最便宜的电动汽车选择，因此 Optiq 的起价可能会低于 60,000 美元，尽管该公司尚未公布这方面的任何细节。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EZnEfP&quot;>;事实上，凯迪拉克尚未提供任何细节无论如何，包括关键规格，如电池范围、尺寸、动力系统选项，如是否具有 AWD 标准、充电速度等。尽管未经证实，Optiq 很可能基于通用汽车的 Ultium 电动汽车平台构建。我们所知道的是它至少会采用橙色，具有正面设计......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593 /cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Tumblr 在变小上下了大赌注</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉色和紫色背景上的 Tumblr 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/V9s3NWknMlUhre6uynnq28E1DjU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875398/STK137_Tumblr_K_Radtke_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;社交网络未能实现其新所有者设定的增长目标2019 年。但它们是否与 Tumblr 最擅长的领域兼容？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social -media-site&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site</id><author><name>阿莱格拉·罗森伯格</name></author></entry></feed>